Hopper Push Messaging API ("The Rabbit")
----------------------------------------

The Hopper Rabbit is a push messaging API to allow travel product providers to stream product offers to the Hopper search index.

All travel product offers available for booking online are indexed in real-time for integration with search results to users on the hopper.com site.

For details about the communication protocols and message schema, please read FlightMessage.pdf and HotelMessage.pdf.

Product offers are stored for up to 3 days, after which offers are purged from the Hopper index.

For details about connecting to the live Hopper Rabbit listener service to include your company's product data on the hopper.com site, please contact Hopper by e-mail.